{"tid":1503482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到有暴徒叫咁做, 大家9月1號一定唔可以入機場!","createTime":"2019-08-25T03:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T19:56:34.000Z","uid":203019,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5ad83ee866042b689c3b72754598aaa40d7371b2","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"聽到有暴徒叫大家咁做, 懇請大家唔好癱瘓機場<br />\n<br />\n機場一定要搞, 仲有<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔好再用「和你飛」呢個名</span></strong>, 我地宜家要<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>癱瘓機場</strong></span>, 唔係齋對外宣傳呀! 記住宜家有禁制令我地好難入機場, 但係正正因為有禁制令, 宜家一號客運大樓落客站得返兩個入口, 上上星期六旅客多少少都逼到出馬路, 只要人夠多足以令真正遊客排返個幾鐘隊. 機鐵都一樣, 你只要搭鐵入黎, 然後塞住入機場個位已經夠做. 藉口都幫大家邐埋, 你排完隊未問下個保安「我想接人機應該去邊個位?」「我想問下宜家仲有冇得睇戲?」「我想去富豪機場酒店點去呀?」自己求求奇作個藉口啦！最後必要時就搗塞馬路, 但要快閃, 果度撤走係其中一個大問題, 逃生路線要手足plan定, 但同樣因為果度有好多遊客, 黑警一定唔會亂咁黎！"},{"pid":"0f97da575860e713c4765e13c04c5df018a8ddd7","tid":1503482,"uid":190285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:51:51.000Z","msg":"（正視聽 1/9見）癱瘓機場並唔係純和理非文宣，係非主動勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502708\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502708</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bf94e4d496eb718f2445c985b3e305bcdf6f6e93","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"228ae25ed58aa921a0943026363c93eb52cd29e6","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"a8941cb722ef2f85318d0b22e11f38b559d77f4b","tid":1503482,"uid":36122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:52:42.000Z","msg":"點解機場post 成日沉??"},{"pid":"9499746b3636143037d7a607db5cefe886f44cac","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"b653e651e693744e0751809106e6fa9593e0f7fe","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"推!"},{"pid":"4a7cdcde80adb7c3329b6d68a3b1b2e481149e7e","tid":1503482,"uid":251660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:53:40.000Z","msg":"【極緊急！只剩最後一日！】<br />\n向白宮聯署阻止曾偉雄出任聯合國總幹事<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions&d=BuHjiuEPdik8Oboe2oqRUCtC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=e7f9142b\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions</a>"},{"pid":"9a61ab55637630108791475e6f5ae36298b5deae","tid":1503482,"uid":276150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"對家痛處一直都在機場！<br />\n小心泛民打手成日嗌人唔好入去！<br />\n<br />\n小心泛民嘅人出嚟扮大台拎喇叭！每次都係，場運動一過佢哋手就玩完！臨門一腳先來出賣香港人，每一次都係！小心"},{"pid":"74bdb883d56d60b3efad5d592482fe3b757b6bcf","tid":1503482,"uid":98842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"【無人講 我講】機場=春袋 建議每個禮拜六日都去<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">9.1去機場 9.7去機場 9.8去機場</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f38acd7482ba76a1d7af918452a6a87cb9c9e7","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fa29b1538225d02eb0eb0c767c98a7705411213","tid":1503482,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:20:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月1 (日) 一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">9月14中秋,未必CALL 到人, 所以</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月7 (六), 9 月8(日) 連續2日一定係機場</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">之後既每個星期六/日 要起碼有一日一定係機場，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乜撚都要讓路!!</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n聽日826 仲有國泰城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7a882257b38d7ab834c063fbeb1816309bd0a6","tid":1503482,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"082e5d6fbccc9c2edbdfe59fcf1c78435ff1ab32","tid":1503482,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"全部人去機場呀屌<br />\n<br />\n想有幾多手足犧牲"},{"pid":"504545eaa4790e9753f5599704e1af718e21712c","tid":1503482,"uid":110970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"9月1 機場<br />\n9月1 機場<br />\n9月1 機場"},{"pid":"7b64bbaedcf36f6718d163041ce5ffd90b5c7e16","tid":1503482,"uid":259284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T04:48:01.000Z","msg":"推，唔好俾政府打手spin走去其他地方"},{"pid":"2ef9b45300cdb016f02afbd79f5db431fd427d79","tid":1503482,"uid":266212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T19:56:34.000Z","msg":"嘩"}]}